                  <paragraph>Diflorasone Diacetate Ointment USP, 0.05% is available in 15 gram (NDC52565-063-15), 30 gram (NDC 52565-063-30) and 60 gram (NDC 52565-063-60) tubes.</paragraph>
               </text>
               <effectiveTime value="20170505"/>
